Package: mELO
Type: Package
Title: Multidimensional ELO Ratings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Lazaridis <davidlaz@gmail.com>
Maintainer: David Lazaridis <davidlaz@gmail.com>
Description: An implementation of DeepMind's multidimensional Elo rating (mELO) 
    approach. The mELO rating system has the desirable properties of being able 
    to handle cyclic interactions and is better behaved in the presence of 
    redundant copies of agents or tasks. This package uses code directly from 
    Alec Stephenson and Jeff Sonas excellent PlayerRatings package (v1.0-3, 2019-02-22).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
